{"id":775,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":775,"title":"Jeremiah 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","Jerusalem will be destroyed because of her iniquity—She will be overrun by a great and cruel nation."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.1","order":"02.25.006.51104"},["b","1"],"O ye children of Benjamin, gather yourselves to flee out of the midst of Jerusalem, and blow the trumpet in Tekoa, and set up a sign of fire in Beth-haccerem: for evil appeareth out of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"north"],", and great destruction."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.2","order":"02.25.006.51105"},["b","2"],"I have likened the daughter of Zion to a comely and delicate",["i","woman."]],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.3","order":"02.25.006.51106"},["b","3"],"The shepherds with their flocks shall come unto her; they shall pitch",["i","their"],"tents against her round about; they shall feed every one in his place."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.4","order":"02.25.006.51107"},["b","4"],"Prepare ye war against her; arise, and let us go up at noon. Woe unto us! for the day goeth away, for the shadows of the evening are stretched out."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.5","order":"02.25.006.51108"},["b","5"],"Arise, and let us go by night, and let us destroy her palaces."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.6","order":"02.25.006.51109"},["b","6"],"¶For thus hath the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts said, Hew ye down trees, and cast a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"mount"],"against Jerusalem: this",["i","is"],"the city to be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"visited"],"; she",["i","is"],"wholly oppression in the midst of her."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.7","order":"02.25.006.51110"},["b","7"],"As a fountain casteth out her waters, so she casteth out her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"wickedness"],":",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"violence"],"and spoil is heard in her; before me continually",["i","is"],"grief and wounds."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.8","order":"02.25.006.51111"},["b","8"],"Be thou instructed, O Jerusalem, lest my soul depart from thee; lest I make thee desolate, a land not inhabited."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.9","order":"02.25.006.51112"},["b","9"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, They shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"throughly"],"glean the remnant of Israel as a vine: turn back thine hand as a grapegatherer",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"into the baskets"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.10","order":"02.25.006.51113"},["b","10"],"To whom shall I speak, and give",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"warning"],", that they may hear? behold, their ear",["i","is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"uncircumcised"],", and they cannot hearken: behold, the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"is unto them a reproach; they have no delight in it."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.11","order":"02.25.006.51114"},["b","11"],"Therefore I am full of the fury of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; I am weary with holding in: I will pour it out upon the children abroad, and upon the assembly of young men together: for even the husband with the wife shall be taken, the aged with",["i","him that is"],"full of days."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.12","order":"02.25.006.51115"},["b","12"],"And their houses shall be turned unto others,",["i","with their"],"fields and wives together: for I will stretch out my hand upon the inhabitants of the land, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.13","order":"02.25.006.51116"},["b","13"],"For from the least of them even unto the greatest of them every one",["i","is"],"given to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"covetousness"],"; and from the prophet even unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"priest"],"every one dealeth falsely."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.14","order":"02.25.006.51117"},["b","14"],"They have healed also the hurt",["i","of the daughter"],"of my people slightly, saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Peace"],", peace; when",["i","there is"],"no peace."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.15","order":"02.25.006.51118"},["b","15"],"Were they ashamed when they had committed abomination? nay, they were not at all ashamed, neither could they blush: therefore they shall fall among them that fall: at the time",["i","that"],"I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"visit"],"them they shall be cast down, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.16","order":"02.25.006.51119"},["b","16"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Stand ye in the ways, and see, and ask for the old",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"paths"],", where",["i","is"],"the good way, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"walk"],"therein, and ye shall find",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"rest"],"for your souls. But they said, We will not walk",["i","therein."]],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.17","order":"02.25.006.51120"},["b","17"],"Also I set",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"watchmen"],"over you,",["i","saying,"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"Hearken"],"to the sound of the trumpet. But they said, We will not hearken."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.18","order":"02.25.006.51121"},["b","18"],"¶Therefore hear, ye nations, and know, O congregation, what",["i","is"],"among them."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.19","order":"02.25.006.51122"},["b","19"],"Hear, O earth: behold, I will bring",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"evil"],"upon this people,",["i","even"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"fruit"],"of their thoughts, because they have not hearkened unto my words, nor to my law, but rejected it."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.20","order":"02.25.006.51123"},["b","20"],"To what purpose cometh there to me incense from Sheba, and the sweet cane from a far country? your burnt offerings",["i","are"],"not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"acceptable"],", nor your sacrifices sweet unto me."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.21","order":"02.25.006.51124"},["b","21"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Behold, I will lay",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"stumblingblocks"],"before this people, and the fathers and the sons together shall fall upon them; the neighbour and his friend shall perish."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.22","order":"02.25.006.51125"},["b","22"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Behold, a people cometh from the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"north"],"country, and a great nation shall be raised from the sides of the earth."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.23","order":"02.25.006.51126"},["b","23"],"They shall lay hold on bow and spear; they",["i","are"],"cruel, and have no mercy; their voice roareth like the sea; and they ride upon horses, set in array as men for war against thee, O daughter of Zion."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.24","order":"02.25.006.51127"},["b","24"],"We have heard the fame thereof: our hands wax feeble: anguish hath taken hold of us,",["i","and"],"pain, as of a woman in travail."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.25","order":"02.25.006.51128"},["b","25"],"Go not forth into the field, nor walk by the way; for the sword of the enemy",["i","and"],"fear",["i","is"],"on every side."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.26","order":"02.25.006.51129"},["b","26"],"¶O daughter of my people, gird",["i","thee"],"with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"sackcloth"],", and wallow thyself in ashes: make thee mourning,",["i","as for"],"an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"only"],"son, most bitter lamentation: for the spoiler shall suddenly come upon us."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.27","order":"02.25.006.51130"},["b","27"],"I have set thee",["i","for"],"a tower",["i","and"],"a fortress among my people, that thou mayest know and try their way."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.28","order":"02.25.006.51131"},["b","28"],"They",["i","are"],"all grievous revolters, walking with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"slanders"],":",["i","they are"],"brass and iron; they",["i","are"],"all corrupters."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.29","order":"02.25.006.51132"},["b","29"],"The bellows",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"are burned"],", the lead is consumed of the fire;",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"the"],"founder melteth in vain: for the wicked are not plucked away."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.30","order":"02.25.006.51133"},["b","30"],"Reprobate silver shall",["i","men"],"call them, because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath rejected them."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.1a","order":"02.25.006.51134"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.14"},"Jer. 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.6"},"4:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.22"},"10:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.6a","order":"02.25.006.51136"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.2"},"Ezek. 4:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.6b","order":"02.25.006.51138"},["b","6b"],["span.small","OR"],"punished."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.7a","order":"02.25.006.51140"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"TG Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.7b","order":"02.25.006.51142"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/20.8"},"Jer. 20:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.9a","order":"02.25.006.51144"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"thoroughly."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.9b","order":"02.25.006.51146"},["b","9b"],["span.small","OR"],"unto the new branches."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.10a","order":"02.25.006.51148"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/warn"},"TG Warn"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.10b","order":"02.25.006.51150"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.51"},"Acts 7:51"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.13a","order":"02.25.006.51152"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covet"},"TG Covet"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.13b","order":"02.25.006.51154"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priestcraft"},"TG Priestcraft"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.14a","order":"02.25.006.51156"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.15a","order":"02.25.006.51158"},["b","15a"],["span.small","OR"],"punish."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.16a","order":"02.25.006.51160"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/18.15"},"Jer. 18:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.16b","order":"02.25.006.51162"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.16c","order":"02.25.006.51164"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rest"},"TG Rest"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.17a","order":"02.25.006.51166"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watchman"},"TG Watchman"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.17b","order":"02.25.006.51168"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/obedience"},"TG Obedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.19a","order":"02.25.006.51170"},["b","19a"],["span.small","OR"],"calamity.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/evil"},"TG Evil"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.19b","order":"02.25.006.51172"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/1.31"},"Prov. 1:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.20a","order":"02.25.006.51174"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.21a","order":"02.25.006.51176"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20"},"Ezek. 3:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.29"},"Mosiah 7:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.22a","order":"02.25.006.51178"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.49"},"Deut. 28:49"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.41.41-43"},"Jer. 50:41 (41–43)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.26a","order":"02.25.006.51180"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apparel"},"TG Apparel"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.26b","order":"02.25.006.51182"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.10"},"Amos 8:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.28a","order":"02.25.006.51184"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/slander"},"TG Slander"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.29a","order":"02.25.006.51186"},["b","29a"],["span.small","OR"],"blew the fire."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.29b","order":"02.25.006.51188"},["b","29b"],["span.small","OR"],"the smelting is in vain."]]}
